# Design System

## Token Access (REQUIRED)
context.colors.primary       — AppColors extension
context.spacing.s16          — AppSpacing extension  
context.textStyles.bodyLarge — AppTypography extension
context.radius.md            — AppRadius extension

Never: Color(0xFF...), 16.0 (raw), TextStyle(fontSize: ...) inline.

## State Widgets (ALL required for data-fetching views)
- Loading: skeleton shimmer (ShimmerWidget) NOT spinner for content areas.
         Inline CircularProgressIndicator ONLY for action buttons.
- Empty:   EmptyStateWidget(title, subtitle, ctaLabel, onCta) — always actionable.
- Error:   ErrorStateWidget(message, onRetry) — always with retry button.
- Use AsyncValue.when(data:, loading:, error:) consistently.

## Component Rules
- Buttons: disabled when isLoading. Prevent double-tap (PATTERN-002).
- Text fields: resizeToAvoidBottomInset: true on Scaffold. SingleChildScrollView wrapper.
- Images: CachedNetworkImage(placeholder: shimmer, errorWidget: ImageErrorPlaceholder).
- Animations: AnimatedContainer, Hero, TweenAnimationBuilder. Never raw Timer.
- Dark mode: every color token must have both light and dark values.
- Tablet: LayoutBuilder + breakpoints. Never hard-coded widths.

## Accessibility (WCAG AA — see also 565-a11y.mdc)
- Minimum tap target: 48x48 logical pixels.
- Text contrast ratio >= 4.5:1 (normal), >= 3:1 (large text).
- All images: semanticsLabel or excludeSemantics.
